xmlText.p: EBay CEO Devin Wenig steps down
Sept 25 (Reuters) - EBay Inc said on Wednesday Chief Executive Officer Devin Wenig has stepped down and the e-commerce company named its finance head Scott Schenkel as interim CEO.
The company said its board will undertake a search for the next CEO. (Reporting by Amal S in Bengaluru; Editing by Shailesh Kuber)
